                    H√£y c√πng kh√°m ph√° th·∫ø gi·ªõi c·ªßa ti·∫øng Hoa. Ch·ªçn m·ªôt m·ª•c ·ªü b√™n tr√°i ƒë·ªÉ b·∫Øt ƒë·∫ßu h·ªçc nh√©!
                </p>
                <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400/bde0fe/000000?text=Ch√†o+M·ª´ng" alt="Ch√†o m·ª´ng b·∫°n ƒë·∫øn v·ªõi trang web h·ªçc ti·∫øng Hoa" class="rounded-lg shadow-md mx-auto">
